sourcesContent: import PropTypes from "prop-types"; import style from './Profile.module.css'; import { Card, Description, Username, Tag, Location, Stats, List, Label} from "./Profile.styled"; export const Profile = ({ username, tag, location, avatar, stats }) => { return ( {username} @{tag} {location} {stats.followers} {stats.views} {stats.likes} ) } Profile.propTypes = { username: PropTypes.string.isRequired, tag: PropTypes.string.isRequired, location: PropTypes.string.isRequired, avatar: PropTypes.string.isRequired, stats: PropTypes.objectOf(PropTypes.number) }
